WEBVTT

00:00:09.405 --> 00:00:14.118 line:90% position:50% align:center
There’s a beautiful gift
that Jehovah provides

00:00:14.118 --> 00:00:18.247 line:90% position:50% align:center
That can help us
grow strong like a tree.

00:00:18.247 --> 00:00:23.043 line:90% position:50% align:center
It is God’s holy spirit
that he gives to us,

00:00:23.043 --> 00:00:27.965 line:90% position:50% align:center
And its fruitage
is easy to see.

00:00:27.965 --> 00:00:32.678 line:10% position:50% align:center
Love we give to our God and our neighbors.

00:00:32.678 --> 00:00:36.932 line:10% position:50% align:center
Joy brightens our face and our mind.

00:00:36.932 --> 00:00:41.604 line:10% position:50% align:center
Peace helps us to always get along.

00:00:41.604 --> 00:00:46.025 line:10% position:50% align:center
Patience helps us endure in hard times.

00:00:46.025 --> 00:00:50.571 line:10% position:50% align:center
Kindness draws other people to us.

00:00:50.571 --> 00:00:55.200 line:10% position:50% align:center
Goodness moves us to help those in need.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:59.955 line:10% position:50% align:center
Faith strengthens our trust in Jehovah.

00:00:59.955 --> 00:01:04.251 line:10% position:50% align:center
Mildness keeps us calm in word and in deed.

00:01:04.251 --> 00:01:09.673 line:10% position:50% align:center
And we all know that self-control is a must.

00:01:12.343 --> 00:01:17.473 line:90% position:50% align:center
And there is so much more
that the spirit can do,

00:01:17.473 --> 00:01:21.685 line:90% position:50% align:center
So let’s pray
for it every day.

00:01:21.685 --> 00:01:26.649 line:90% position:50% align:center
Then this beautiful fruitage
will show in our lives,

00:01:26.649 --> 00:01:30.444 line:90% position:50% align:center
